title: “Buffalo Billion has been a phenomenal success”
text: Gov. Andrew Cuomo today defended the money the state has doled out to Buffalo amid subpoenas issued by federal prosecutors seeking details about the contracts for the Buffalo Billion project. Reports surfaced earlier this month that U.S. Attorney Preet Bharara has subpoenaed records from the SUNY Polytechnic Institute and other state agencies over lucrative contracts [...] The post Cuomo: " Buffalo Billion has been a phenomenal success " appeared first on Politics on the Hudson.
